<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <style>
        body { font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
        .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; border-radius: 12px; }
        .header { text-align: center; padding-bottom: 20px; border-bottom: 2px solid #8b5cf6; }
        .content { padding: 20px 0; }
        .footer { font-size: 12px; text-align: center; color: #718096; margin-top: 20px; }
        .title { font-size: 18px; font-weight: bold; color: #1e293b; }
        .details { background: #f5f3ff; padding: 15px; border-radius: 8px; margin-top: 10px; }
        .priority { display: inline-block; padding: 4px 12px; border-radius: 9999px; font-size: 12px; font-weight: bold; }
        .priority-high { background: #fee2e2; color: #991b1b; }
        .priority-medium { background: #fef3c7; color: #92400e; }
        .priority-low { background: #dcfce7; color: #166534; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h2>New Task Assigned</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>Hello <strong>{{name}}</strong>,</p>
            <p>You have been assigned a new task in the system.</p>
            
            <div class="details">
                <p class="title">{{title}}</p>
                <p>Priority: <span class="priority priority-{{priority}}">{{priority}}</span></p>
                <p>Deadline: <strong>{{deadline}}</strong></p>
            </div>
            
            <p>Please log in to the dashboard to view full details and start working.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>Keep up the great work!</p>
            <p>© CRM System</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
